<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .invitation-code {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007AFF;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .custom-message {
      border-left: 4px solid #007AFF;
      padding-left: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="https://tiktoktoe.app/logo.png" alt="TikTokToe Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>Welcome to TikTokToe Beta!</h1>
  </div>

  <p>Hi{{#if inviteeHandle}} @{{inviteeHandle}}{{/if}},</p>

  <p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> (@{{inviterHandle}}) has invited you to join the TikTokToe beta program!</p>

  {{#if customMessage}}
  <div class="custom-message">
    "{{customMessage}}"
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  <p>TikTokToe is a next-generation social platform built on the AT Protocol, offering:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Decentralized social networking</li>
    <li>Full data ownership and portability</li>
    <li>Rich media sharing capabilities</li>
    <li>Advanced content discovery</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Your exclusive beta invitation code is:</p>
  <div class="invitation-code">
    {{invitationCode}}
  </div>

  <p style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="https://tiktoktoe.app/beta/join?code={{invitationCode}}" class="button">
      Join the Beta
    </a>
  </p>

  <p>To get started:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Click the button above or visit <a href="https://tiktoktoe.app/beta">tiktoktoe.app/beta</a></li>
    <li>Enter your invitation code</li>
    <li>Create your account or connect with your existing AT Protocol identity</li>
    <li>Start exploring and providing feedback!</li>
  </ol>

  <p>As a beta tester, you'll get:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Early access to new features</li>
    <li>Direct communication with our development team</li>
    <li>Influence over the platform's development</li>
    <li>Exclusive beta tester badge</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This invitation expires in 7 days. Questions? Reply to this email or contact us at beta@tiktoktoe.app</p>
    <p>TikTokToe, Inc. â€¢ Built on the AT Protocol</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
